Synopsis:

Crown Princess Rhaenyra Targaryen returns to her Dragonstone castle with her family - her husband Daemon, her sons Jace and Luke, and her stepdaughters Baela and Rhaena - after attending a royal dinner with her father the king Viserys I and the Green faction. Upon their arrival, Rhaenyra discovers that Jace and Luke performed a magical ritual to change their appearances, hoping to avoid rumors about their illegitimacy.
As a consequence of the magical ritual, younger versions of Rhaenyra (Nyra) and Daemon (Daemion) from seventeen years ago are inadvertently brought into the present, along with Nyra’s sworn guard Criston Cole. Adult Rhaenyra decides to help her past self and Daemion return to their time, but tensions arise as the young Nyra and Daemion intend to marry each other right here.
Nyra and Daemion’s budding relationship complicates matters further, as the existing relationships and futures of the family are put at risk. Baela and Rhaena fear their existence will be erased if their father, Daemon, ends up with Nyra instead of their mother Laena. They ally with Ser Criston, Jace and Luke to prevent Nyra and Daemion from marrying.
The conflict intensifies when it is revealed that Jace and Luke’s existence is directly tied to Nyra and Daemion. If they don’t conceive the boys within a few weeks, Jace and Luke will cease to exist. Torn between personal happiness and their duties to the family, Rhaenyra and Daemon strive to preserve the delicate balance.
 Readers will be captivated by the struggles of Rhaenyra, Daemon, Nyra, and Daemion as they fight to save their intertwined futures while navigating treacherous waters of passion, loyalty, and duty.

Character Name: Rhaenyra Targaryen
- Main goal: Ensure the continued existence of her children and maintain the well-being of her family;
- Motivations: Love for her children, desire for personal happiness, obligation to her current family, and a desire to maintain her claim as queen;

Character Name: Nyra (18 year old, Young Rhaenyra from the past)
- Main goal: Marry Daemion (Young Daemon) and return back to her own timeline
- Motivations: Love for Daemion, desire for personal happiness, and fear of her future self’s fate;

Character Name: Daemon Targaryen
- Main goal: Help Daemion and Nyra’s relationship while also searching for a magical way to make Rhaenyra the mother of his daughters;
- Motivations: Love for Rhaenyra and desire for to keep his family secure;

Character Name: Daemion (34 year  old, Younger Daemon from the past)
- Main goal: Marry Nyra, conceive Jace and Luke, return safely back to their time;
- Motivations: A desire for starting a family, to father future heirs to the throne, a desire for a role of Nyra’s consort;

